{"tid":242654,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"高木同學53-54","createTime":"2017-05-14T05:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T06:41:13.000Z","uid":34105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97629d981ab3ed0fd839621ccf504f360c56369f","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"53<br />\n<a href=\"http://mangapark.me/manga/karakai-jouzu-no-takagi-san-yamamoto-souichirou/s5/c53/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmangapark.me%2Fmanga%2Fkarakai-jouzu-no-takagi-san-yamamoto-souichirou%2Fs5%2Fc53%2F1&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=532f9202\" target=\"_blank\">http://mangapark.me/manga/karakai-jouzu-no-takagi-san-yamamoto-souichirou/s5/c53/1</a><br />\n畀fd斷正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n54<br />\n<a href=\"http://mangapark.me/manga/karakai-jouzu-no-takagi-san-yamamoto-souichirou/s5/c54/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmangapark.me%2Fmanga%2Fkarakai-jouzu-no-takagi-san-yamamoto-souichirou%2Fs5%2Fc54%2F1&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=48044238\" target=\"_blank\">http://mangapark.me/manga/karakai-jouzu-no-takagi-san-yamamoto-souichirou/s5/c54/1</a><br />\n次次高木同學整蠱完西片再畀返甜頭佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上兩集體能測試都冇咁甜,但今次正"},{"pid":"362f58f0196a0449fce8cd61531cc1ec6c3c0341","tid":242654,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C_rpwnVUAAAJ3Mi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC_rpwnVUAAAJ3Mi.jpg&h=c19e0cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://figsoku.net/blog-entry-67287.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffigsoku.net%2Fblog-entry-67287.html&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=cf5bb6d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://figsoku.net/blog-entry-67287.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1498e2eb4e87a6fc69c3a4f2909c2bd5a6afc73e","tid":242654,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"想問下漫畫人集數係唔係亂晒?"},{"pid":"5d733d9c487f33f16af235a8fe540c3196ca1279","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下漫畫人集數係唔係亂晒?</blockquote><br />\n冇,本身就唔跟時序,好似51,52係過左一年,48先講番當初入學兩個點識"},{"pid":"0c6771c0883031708f597c4e91615732520e7655","tid":242654,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:33:23.000Z","msg":"甜到糖尿病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01926220f26b4fd234a585cbb33f7b7e30eb9a56","tid":242654,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下漫畫人集數係唔係亂晒?</blockquote><br />\n冇,本身就唔跟時序,好似51,52係過左一年,48先講番當初入學兩個點識</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n搞到我鬼死咁期待夏祭 仲以為冇咗"},{"pid":"648ab6c0815bddfa0c54cbd88295a516ab2ba828","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下漫畫人集數係唔係亂晒?</blockquote><br />\n冇,本身就唔跟時序,好似51,52係過左一年,48先講番當初入學兩個點識</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n搞到我鬼死咁期待夏祭 仲以為冇咗</blockquote><br />\n我果時都想佢出夏祭,點知冇出,反而杏子妹妹就有畫夏祭"},{"pid":"063af1c3f409dbd3acddf80fb6ab27bb7fa6b761","tid":242654,"uid":106520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"繼續畫杏子妹妹就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e903a33c5a7772cf81f2595681dae7dd46585c2b","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續畫杏子妹妹就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想.好彩最後都係同日日野一齊.<br />\nbtw,高木同學三人組白色頭係日日野表妹黎<br />\n三人組自己都有套漫畫,有4本,叫&quot;あしたは土曜日&quot;,不過搵唔到邊度有得睇"},{"pid":"002816aedf8465db7096b8da73dc12283caf880a","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"53漢化已出"},{"pid":"37f382793e93bdb745d4d9eefa948826910af6f9","tid":242654,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"高木搞咁大輪野其實就係想西片食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">個飯團</span></span>"},{"pid":"573aa87ce7faedb285931b92987ad51d395ff6c1","tid":242654,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高木搞咁大輪野其實就係想西片食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">個飯團</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我覺得高木都係玩玩下先鍾意佢"},{"pid":"978f2e0b914fdc5d04dac7b099052418b14457df","tid":242654,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高木搞咁大輪野其實就係想西片食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">個飯團</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我覺得高木都係玩玩下先鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n曾幾何時我都做過西片依個角色<br />\n可惜小學果時鬼知咩叫愛情咩"},{"pid":"207cd00fef39af93c6835d24721b36a8232cc711","tid":242654,"uid":23673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>繼續畫杏子妹妹就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想.好彩最後都係同日日野一齊.<br />\nbtw,高木同學三人組白色頭係日日野表妹黎<br />\n三人組自己都有套漫畫,有4本,叫&quot;あしたは土曜日&quot;,不過搵唔到邊度有得睇</blockquote><br />\n其實點解杏子會變左疆屍？"},{"pid":"e9cfee5089e438758524a04491f19b8a2149cf8d","tid":242654,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:42:09.000Z","msg":"墨鏡都裂開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cec4ca5e1722f7aeaf2f9d3c3f5130a646bc26","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>高木搞咁大輪野其實就係想西片食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">個飯團</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我覺得高木都係玩玩下先鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n曾幾何時我都做過西片依個角色<br />\n可惜小學果時鬼知咩叫愛情咩</blockquote><br />\n高木西片係中一(52集應該係中二,因為過左一年)<br />\n西片有一點幾貼近現實青春期青少年,有時都會懷疑下高木係咁鍾意自己,自己又係唔係鍾意左高木,唔似一d漫畫個男仔遲鈍個女仔做乜野佢少少都唔覺得奇怪"},{"pid":"48618453a88dafb36e738c6e8647aff64c3cb7d4","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>繼續畫杏子妹妹就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想.好彩最後都係同日日野一齊.<br />\nbtw,高木同學三人組白色頭係日日野表妹黎<br />\n三人組自己都有套漫畫,有4本,叫&quot;あしたは土曜日&quot;,不過搵唔到邊度有得睇</blockquote><br />\n其實點解杏子會變左疆屍？</blockquote><br />\n冇解釋,純粹安個咁既設定特別d掛<br />\n不過如果杏子紅得起我諗都有機會解既"},{"pid":"8b306fe51c6722a65e766f4f64503b112137629a","tid":242654,"uid":45966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e5ebc9a909545f3a16f7de07f3438a1e552fbe76","tid":242654,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"肯扑野味姐"},{"pid":"10d6cdc70888b2e5356ba052d2554059e3ef0378","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯扑野味姐</blockquote><br />\n衰11"},{"pid":"6425b86c80fea06ca65e6bbb0f731fffe8dad6a9","tid":242654,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯扑野味姐</blockquote><br />\n衰11"},{"pid":"fe563d345312d1cdb477fc8daeaa7b078f98bc3c","tid":242654,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"條淫雞係咁引西片<br />\n西片都唔識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6b74d52ef890cac1544de7f835923450ac723d","tid":242654,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"擅長撚狗的高木同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa430d86dd1c203bc320f43bdeb8c608a671f65","tid":242654,"uid":29442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"是擅長捉弄的女朋友呢"},{"pid":"a8c413af8fa61ef9e50720e1a34fa58dc7334662","tid":242654,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"個作者好似好鍾意中分髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}